snippet.title: The personality COINCIDENCES of Meghan and Amber Heard
snippet.description:
If I asked you the question, "What does Meghan Markle have in common with Amber Heard"? I'm sure that the word 'narcissism' will pop up more than a couple times.

And I was talking in another video about the types of narcissism and someone suggested that I make one about this classification.
